<h2>Effective Date: 18/02/2026</h2>

<p>
IGT PDF Editor (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our mobile application.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
<p>
Our app does not require you to create an account. We do not directly collect personal information such as:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Name</li>
    <li>Email address</li>
    <li>Phone number</li>
</ul>
<p>
However, certain features involve third-party services described below.
</p>

<h3>1.2 PDF Files and Documents</h3>
<ul>
    <li>PDF files you open or edit remain on your device.</li>
    <li>We do not upload, store, or transmit your documents to our servers.</li>
    <li>All editing is performed locally on your device.</li>
</ul>

<h3>1.3 Advertising (AdMob)</h3>
<p>
The app uses Google AdMob to display advertisements to free users.
</p>
<p>AdMob may collect:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Device identifiers</li>
    <li>IP address</li>
    <li>Advertising ID</li>
    <li>App interaction data</li>
</ul>
<p>
This data is used to provide personalized or non-personalized ads.
</p>
<p>
For more information, see:
<br>
<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">
Google Privacy Policy
</a>
</p>

<h3>1.4 In-App Purchases (Premium Subscription)</h3>
<p>
Premium subscriptions are processed through Google Play Billing.
</p>
<ul>
    <li>We do not collect or store credit card information.</li>
    <li>We do not collect or store payment details.</li>
</ul>
<p>
All transactions are securely handled by Google Play.
</p>

<h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Provide PDF editing features</li>
    <li>Show advertisements (free users)</li>
    <li>Process premium subscriptions</li>
    <li>Improve app stability and performance</li>
</ul>
<p>We do not sell personal data.</p>

<h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
<ul>
    <li>PDF files are stored locally on your device.</li>
    <li>Edited exports are saved to your device storage.</li>
    <li>No cloud storage is used.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
<p>We do not share your personal information except:</p>
<ul>
    <li>With Google AdMob for advertising</li>
    <li>With Google Play for subscription processing</li>
    <li>If required by law</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>
This app is not directed toward children under 13.  
We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.
</p>

<h2>6. Your Rights (GDPR / CCPA)</h2>
<p>Depending on your location, you may have rights to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request data access</li>
    <li>Request deletion</li>
    <li>Opt-out of personalized ads</li>
</ul>
<p>
You can manage ad preferences via your device settings:<br>
<strong>Settings → Google → Ads</strong>
</p>

<h2>7. Security</h2>
<p>
We implement reasonable safeguards to protect your data.  
However, no method of electronic transmission is 100% secure.
</p>

<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.  
Changes will be posted within the app listing or website.
</p>

<h2>9. Contact Information</h2>
<p>
If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, contact:
</p>
<p>
Email: info.igttech@gmail.com<br>
Developer: Seth Iradukunda
</p>

